Dialogue: 0,0:00:01.80,0:00:03.02,main,Rishe,0,0,0,,Thank you.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:04.65,0:00:08.52,main,Rishe,0,0,0,,I heard that Sir Kamil and \NElsie won't receive punishment.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:09.27,0:00:11.90,main,Theodore,0,0,0,,It's nothing to thank me for.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:12.21,0:00:15.60,main,Rishe,0,0,0,,While I'm thinking of it, I heard that \Nthe policies for improving the slums
Dialogue: 0,0:00:15.60,0:00:19.54,main,Rishe,0,0,0,,are going to move forward under \Nyour leadership, Prince Theodore.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:21.16,0:00:24.00,main,Theodore,0,0,0,,My brother asked me if I wanted to do it.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:24.00,0:00:28.29,main,Rishe,0,0,0,,Then, does that mean the both of you \Nwill be attending to official matters?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:29.49,0:00:32.03,main,Theodore,0,0,0,,Well, I suppose it does.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:32.78,0:00:36.55,main,Theodore,0,0,0,,Now, you didn't take the trouble to \Ncome here just to say that, did you?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:37.39,0:00:40.43,main,Rishe,0,0,0,,Actually, I have a favor to ask of you.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:43.02,0:00:43.67,main,Theodore,0,0,0,,What?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:44.31,0:00:48.19,main,Rishe,0,0,0,,This is something which will be \Nessential for your brother as well.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:48.65,0:00:53.19,main,Theodore,0,0,0,,What do I do? I have no idea \Nwhat my sister-in-law is saying.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:53.60,0:00:56.13,main,Rishe,0,0,0,,Please, Prince Theodore.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:30.56,0:02:32.35,top,Diana,0,0,0,,The preparations are complete.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:34.58,0:02:36.51,main,Rishe,0,0,0,,I'll be off now.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:36.78,0:02:37.72,main,maids,0,0,0,,Yes, my lady!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:42.23,0:02:45.07,main,Oliver,0,0,0,,An official letter from the \NKingdom of Coyolles has arrived.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:57.87,0:02:58.71,main,Arnold,0,0,0,,Come in.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:01.20,0:03:03.93,main,Rishe,0,0,0,,How are you faring, Prince Arnold?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:03.93,0:03:07.79,main,Rishe,0,0,0,,Thank you for granting me your \Ntime in spite of how busy you are.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:08.08,0:03:10.29,main,Arnold,0,0,0,,What sort of business brings you here?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:10.29,0:03:14.28,main,Arnold,0,0,0,,You seem too tense to have come \Nsimply to see your fiancé's face.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:20.62,0:03:23.80,main,Rishe,0,0,0,,A room has been prepared for you \Nat the villa, Your Highness.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:24.16,0:03:24.95,main,Arnold,0,0,0,,What?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:25.69,0:03:29.28,main,Rishe,0,0,0,,If you have the time, may I \Nshow you the room now?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:29.28,0:03:32.31,main,Arnold,0,0,0,,Why would this errand make you so nervous?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:32.61,0:03:36.06,main,Rishe,0,0,0,,My maids have worked \Neagerly and diligently on it.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:36.06,0:03:38.91,main,Rishe,0,0,0,,It's almost like a graduation exam for them.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:39.57,0:03:44.28,main,Rishe,0,0,0,,However, I can confidently assert that the \Nroom they've prepared is quite lovely.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:45.36,0:03:49.79,main,Arnold,0,0,0,,I had thought it was your wish \Nto live in that villa alone.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:49.79,0:03:51.40,main,Rishe,0,0,0,,Of course not!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:51.40,0:03:55.17,main,Rishe,0,0,0,,I want to live there with you, Prince Arnold.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:56.52,0:03:57.73,main,Arnold,0,0,0,,I see.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:58.40,0:04:01.30,main,Arnold,0,0,0,,It seems you're plotting \Nsomething amusing yet again.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:01.30,0:04:03.59,main,Rishe,0,0,0,,You make me sound awful!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:04.03,0:04:05.05,main,Arnold,0,0,0,,Very well.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:05.40,0:04:07.51,main,Arnold,0,0,0,,I'll go along with your scheme.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:07.51,0:04:09.68,main,Arnold,0,0,0,,Thanks to you, my mood has improved.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:10.59,0:04:12.43,main,Rishe,0,0,0,,Your mood?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:12.43,0:04:13.48,main,Arnold,0,0,0,,Let's go.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:19.52,0:04:21.19,main,Oliver,0,0,0,,Thank you.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:25.39,0:04:27.53,main,Rishe,0,0,0,,This is your private bedroom, Your Highness.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:28.08,0:04:31.05,main,Rishe,0,0,0,,What do you think? It's a \Nsplendid room, isn't it?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:31.05,0:04:32.83,main,Arnold,0,0,0,,Very impressive.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:33.06,0:04:36.71,main,Arnold,0,0,0,,This villa has been left \Nabandoned for many years.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:36.96,0:04:39.17,main,Arnold,0,0,0,,You've been here a mere three weeks.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:39.17,0:04:40.91,main,Arnold,0,0,0,,To think you've already\Nimproved it this much.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:40.91,0:04:42.58,main,Rishe,0,0,0,,Thank you!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:42.58,0:04:44.84,main,Arnold,0,0,0,,You taught the novices starting \Nwith the basics, didn't you?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:44.84,0:04:48.97,main,Rishe,0,0,0,,Yes. Once they've learned a trade, they'll \Nbe able to make their living anywhere.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:48.97,0:04:50.99,main,Arnold,0,0,0,,And they'll gain something else, too.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:52.48,0:04:53.48,main,Arnold,0,0,0,,Pride.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:54.01,0:04:57.55,main,Arnold,0,0,0,,When they accomplish their work \Nand earn the praise of another,
Dialogue: 0,0:04:57.55,0:04:58.88,main,Arnold,0,0,0,,it will give them a sense of pride.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:59.51,0:05:02.19,main,Arnold,0,0,0,,That sort of pride can help a person \Nmake the most of themselves.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:02.70,0:05:06.57,main,Arnold,0,0,0,,You have a talent for giving \Npeople a sense of self-respect.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:10.28,0:05:12.98,main,Arnold,0,0,0,,That's the expression you \Nmake when I compliment you?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:14.27,0:05:17.32,main,Rishe,0,0,0,,You're teasing me, aren't you?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:17.32,0:05:19.42,main,Arnold,0,0,0,,It may not seem like it, \Nbut it's heartfelt praise.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:19.91,0:05:21.57,main,Rishe,0,0,0,,Well, it's just too bad for you.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:21.57,0:05:25.97,main,Rishe,0,0,0,,Even if it's a lie, receiving a compliment \Nfrom you makes me very happy.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:28.65,0:05:32.62,main,Rishe,0,0,0,,Out of the whole villa, this \Nroom gets the best light.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:38.08,0:05:40.59,main,Rishe,0,0,0,,The wind feels wonderful \Nwhen you open the window,
Dialogue: 0,0:05:40.59,0:05:42.82,main,Rishe,0,0,0,,so it's perfect for an afternoon \Nnap, don't you think?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:43.18,0:05:45.58,main,Arnold,0,0,0,,I never return to my chambers during the day.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:46.14,0:05:48.45,main,Arnold,0,0,0,,This room is next to yours, isn't it?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:48.45,0:05:52.58,main,Rishe,0,0,0,,Yes. I thought that would \Nmake it easier for the guards.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:52.80,0:05:54.00,main,Arnold,0,0,0,,And for me.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:54.00,0:05:54.77,main,Rishe,0,0,0,,What?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:54.77,0:05:57.70,main,Arnold,0,0,0,,Because I'll get wind of your \Nreckless behavior beforehand.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:57.70,0:06:01.46,main,Rishe,0,0,0,,I'm planning to spend my time lazing about, \Nso I won't be doing anything reckless.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:02.96,0:06:04.46,main,Rishe,0,0,0,,Not much, anyway.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:04.46,0:06:05.63,main,Arnold,0,0,0,,Idiot.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:06.14,0:06:07.75,main,Arnold,0,0,0,,You're free to do what you want,
Dialogue: 0,0:06:07.75,0:06:10.32,main,Arnold,0,0,0,,but don't do anything as reckless \Nas you did the other day.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:10.32,0:06:11.93,main,Rishe,0,0,0,,I'm very sorry.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:13.01,0:06:17.05,main,Rishe,0,0,0,,Speaking of which, do you remember what we \Ntalked about at the party the other evening?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:17.05,0:06:17.85,main,Arnold,0,0,0,,What do you mean?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:18.42,0:06:21.48,main,Rishe,0,0,0,,When you said that you wanted \Nto try sparring with me.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:23.47,0:06:26.79,flashback,Arnold,0,0,0,,It might be worthwhile for me to \Ntry sparring with you one day.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:26.79,0:06:29.28,flashback,Rishe,0,0,0,,I would like that very much!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:29.94,0:06:32.24,main,Arnold,0,0,0,,Yes, we did say that.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:32.24,0:06:33.75,main,Rishe,0,0,0,,Just once would be enough.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:33.75,0:06:35.62,main,Rishe,0,0,0,,Would you instruct me?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:35.62,0:06:40.37,main,Rishe,0,0,0,,Teach me using the special training methods \NYour Highness and the imperial knights use.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:41.34,0:06:43.63,main,Arnold,0,0,0,,What makes you say that they're special?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:44.33,0:06:48.80,main,Rishe,0,0,0,,Since coming to this palace, I've watched \Neveryone train a number of times,
Dialogue: 0,0:06:48.80,0:06:53.51,main,Rishe,0,0,0,,but Your Highness' and the imperial knights' \Nmovement is clearly different from the rest.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:56.68,0:06:57.68,main,Arnold,0,0,0,,All right.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:57.68,0:07:00.35,main,Rishe,0,0,0,,What? Are you sure?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:00.97,0:07:05.11,main,Arnold,0,0,0,,I did promise to do anything \Nyou wished, after all.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:05.11,0:07:08.32,main,Rishe,0,0,0,,Oh, um... Thank you.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:08.88,0:07:10.86,main,Rishe,0,0,0,,That makes me incredibly happy.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:11.40,0:07:12.74,main,Arnold,0,0,0,,Happy?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:13.22,0:07:20.75,main,Rishe,0,0,0,,As far as I know, your sword work is the \Nmost beautiful, most powerful in all the world.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:22.03,0:07:23.99,main,Arnold,0,0,0,,In all the world, huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:24.76,0:07:27.00,main,Rishe,0,0,0,,Th-That's just a turn of phrase, of course!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:27.59,0:07:32.32,main,Arnold,0,0,0,,A skill that's only meant for killing \Npeople can't possibly be beautiful.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:32.77,0:07:33.89,main,Rishe,0,0,0,,Your Highness...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:35.48,0:07:37.67,main,Arnold,0,0,0,,I'll head to the practice \Ngrounds ahead of you.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:37.67,0:07:39.50,main,Arnold,0,0,0,,Change into some clothes\Nthat you can move in.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:43.37,0:07:46.60,main,Rishe,0,0,0,,Is this how you always practice?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:46.60,0:07:48.40,main,Arnold,0,0,0,,Not always.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:48.40,0:07:52.15,main,Arnold,0,0,0,,Once you've acquired an incorrect habit, \Nit's too late to do anything about it.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:52.15,0:07:56.96,main,Rishe,0,0,0,,The arm and leg restraints are meant to \Nhelp closely mimic battlefield conditions,
Dialogue: 0,0:07:56.96,0:07:59.66,main,Rishe,0,0,0,,so that you can continue to fight \Neven if you've lost a limb.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:00.21,0:08:02.29,main,Rishe,0,0,0,,That's what this training is for, isn't it?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:03.33,0:08:06.29,main,Arnold,0,0,0,,As usual, your observations are impressive.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:06.74,0:08:09.30,main,Arnold,0,0,0,,Even if my arm is ripped off, \NI'll keep swinging my sword.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:09.30,0:08:12.05,main,Arnold,0,0,0,,Even if my leg is shattered, \NI'll continue to advance.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:12.05,0:08:14.33,main,Arnold,0,0,0,,And even if I should lose both my eyes,
Dialogue: 0,0:08:14.33,0:08:17.55,main,Arnold,0,0,0,,I'll keep looking, to the very last, \Nfor a path to cut down my enemy.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:18.00,0:08:21.36,main,Arnold,0,0,0,,Doing that will lead to \Na way for me to survive.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:21.96,0:08:26.77,main,Rishe,0,0,0,,I've heard that a knight's path \Npursues nobility and beauty.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:27.53,0:08:31.38,main,Rishe,0,0,0,,However, they will find a way to survive, no \Nmatter how unsightly their struggles may be.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:31.38,0:08:33.46,main,Rishe,0,0,0,,It's to survive that they kill their enemies.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:34.11,0:08:36.95,main,Rishe,0,0,0,,That way of thinking comes from \NYour Highness, doesn't it?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:38.10,0:08:40.45,italics,Rishe; internal,0,0,0,,It's no wonder I was no match for him.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:40.45,0:08:42.11,main,Arnold,0,0,0,,Don't worry.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:42.11,0:08:46.96,main,Arnold,0,0,0,,I have no intention of injuring an opponent \Nwho's preparing for their marriage ceremony.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:49.50,0:08:54.09,main,Rishe,0,0,0,,If I win, will you give me an answer \Nto one question, no matter what it is?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:55.01,0:09:01.35,main,Rishe,0,0,0,,In exchange, if I lose, I'll grant one wish \Nof Your Highness', no matter what it may be.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:02.87,0:09:04.10,main,Arnold,0,0,0,,Very well.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:04.30,0:09:06.82,main,Rishe,0,0,0,,Then, if you would.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:07.35,0:09:08.50,main,Kamil,0,0,0,,Begin!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:11.54,0:09:14.26,italics,Rishe; internal,0,0,0,,The longer our exchange of blows lasts, \Nthe greater my disadvantage.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:20.08,0:09:21.56,italics,Rishe; internal,0,0,0,,A frontal attack!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:26.97,0:09:29.37,main,Arnold,0,0,0,,What's wrong? Is that all you've got?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:30.54,0:09:32.75,italics,Rishe; internal,0,0,0,,My center of balance is unstable.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:32.75,0:09:36.26,italics,Rishe; internal,0,0,0,,My instincts are trying to make me move \Nthe way I do when I can use my left arm.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:36.92,0:09:40.76,italics,Rishe; internal,0,0,0,,If I adjust my center of \Nbalance... my reach will change.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:41.70,0:09:43.43,italics,Rishe; internal,0,0,0,,I'll have to step in closer!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:45.60,0:09:47.85,main,Arnold,0,0,0,,Your movement's dulled!\N Don't rely on strength alone!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:48.45,0:09:49.86,main,Arnold,0,0,0,,Your footwork is growing careless!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:50.23,0:09:51.86,main,Arnold,0,0,0,,Make use of your nimbleness.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:52.27,0:09:53.44,main,Arnold,0,0,0,,Step in farther!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:54.36,0:09:55.49,main,Arnold,0,0,0,,Another step.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:55.49,0:09:56.11,main,Arnold,0,0,0,,Still not there.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:56.11,0:09:57.11,main,Arnold,0,0,0,,You see?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:59.82,0:10:01.81,italics,Rishe; internal,0,0,0,,He really is impressive.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:01.81,0:10:03.72,italics,Rishe; internal,0,0,0,,In this short exchange of blows,
Dialogue: 0,0:10:03.72,0:10:06.83,italics,Rishe; internal,0,0,0,,he's telling me exactly what \Npoints I need to improve upon.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:09.83,0:10:14.81,main,Kamil,0,0,0,,It's only been a little while since Lady \NRishe crossed swords with His Highness, but...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:14.81,0:10:18.59,main,Dennis,0,0,0,,You're right. In the blink of an eye, \Nher movements have already improved.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:26.22,0:10:27.74,italics,Rishe; internal,0,0,0,,Next, he'll come from above!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:34.65,0:10:37.39,italics,Rishe; internal,0,0,0,,The same move as back then.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:38.00,0:10:42.14,italics,Rishe; internal,0,0,0,,But even if I understand what's \Nhappening, my body can't keep up.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:43.37,0:10:47.28,main,Arnold,0,0,0,,Earlier, you said that my sword \Nwas the most powerful, didn't you?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:47.88,0:10:52.67,main,Arnold,0,0,0,,But that movement just now was that of \Nsomeone who knows of a person stronger than me.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:53.60,0:10:57.99,main,Arnold,0,0,0,,Even as you're sparring with me, you're \Nthinking of that person, aren't you?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:59.70,0:11:00.91,main,Arnold,0,0,0,,How enviable.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:02.72,0:11:04.96,main,Arnold,0,0,0,,I'm on the verge of becoming jealous.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:06.16,0:11:07.64,main,Rishe,0,0,0,,You jest.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:08.11,0:11:14.56,main,Rishe,0,0,0,,As I told you, you are the strongest \Nperson I know, Prince Arnold.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:15.48,0:11:20.58,italics,Rishe; internal,0,0,0,,It's true. The prince of five years in the \Nfuture was even stronger than he is now.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:20.58,0:11:22.72,italics,Rishe; internal,0,0,0,,He was cruel and overwhelmingly formidable.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:25.23,0:11:26.10,main,Arnold,0,0,0,,Come at me.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:27.30,0:11:29.29,main,Arnold,0,0,0,,Focus on me a just little more.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:48.78,0:11:49.52,main,Rishe,0,0,0,,I'm not done yet!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:04.68,0:12:06.31,main,Arnold,0,0,0,,Very impressive.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:06.31,0:12:08.83,main,Arnold,0,0,0,,I wasn't planning on moving a single step.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:10.01,0:12:14.08,main,Rishe,0,0,0,,It seems you limited yourself \Nquite a bit for my sake.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:14.58,0:12:17.59,main,Arnold,0,0,0,,Though it appears I greatly \Nunderestimated you.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:18.70,0:12:21.12,main,Rishe,0,0,0,,Thank you for your instruction.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:22.56,0:12:26.34,main,Arnold,0,0,0,,You'll do any one thing \NI want, is that right?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:26.34,0:12:28.84,main,Rishe,0,0,0,,Yes. Ask whatever you like of me.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:28.84,0:12:30.35,main,Rishe,0,0,0,,I won't go back on my word.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:31.56,0:12:34.72,main,Arnold,0,0,0,,Then, clear your afternoon \Nfor two days from now.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:34.72,0:12:35.98,main,Arnold,0,0,0,,We're going into town.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:35.98,0:12:39.77,main,Rishe,0,0,0,,Into town? To do what?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:39.77,0:12:41.26,main,Arnold,0,0,0,,I'll tell you when the time comes.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:44.01,0:12:46.11,main,Arnold,0,0,0,,What's wrong? Stand up.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:49.99,0:12:51.62,main,Rishe,0,0,0,,Um...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:52.22,0:12:54.97,main,Rishe,0,0,0,,I'm going to stay like this a little longer.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:54.97,0:12:57.25,main,Rishe,0,0,0,,Please go ahead and return without me.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:57.25,0:12:58.16,main,Arnold,0,0,0,,Why?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:00.48,0:13:05.88,main,Rishe,0,0,0,,The truth is... due to our sparring just \Nnow, my arms and legs are shaking.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:06.36,0:13:07.53,main,Arnold,0,0,0,,What?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:07.53,0:13:10.14,main,Rishe,0,0,0,,It seems my body wasn't able to keep up.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:10.57,0:13:13.07,main,Rishe,0,0,0,,So I'm going to rest a little.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:15.09,0:13:16.27,main,Rishe,0,0,0,,Your Highness?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:16.90,0:13:20.40,main,Arnold,0,0,0,,I'll only be touching you through my \Ngloves, so it won't be a problem, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:21.03,0:13:21.48,main,Rishe,0,0,0,,What?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:21.48,0:13:22.98,main,Rishe,0,0,0,,What? Wait, Your Highness!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:31.03,0:13:32.64,main,Arnold,0,0,0,,Stop struggling. You'll fall.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:32.64,0:13:34.49,main,Rishe,0,0,0,,Um, it's just that this is...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:34.49,0:13:35.41,main,Arnold,0,0,0,,You can't stand, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:35.41,0:13:38.29,main,Rishe,0,0,0,,I can stand! I will stand! \NPlease put me down!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:38.29,0:13:40.89,main,Arnold,0,0,0,,I can't go back and just leave \Nmy fiancée behind, can I?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:40.89,0:13:43.63,main,Rishe,0,0,0,,That may be true, but...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:45.52,0:13:48.74,main,Arnold,0,0,0,,While I'm thinking of it, \Nwhat did you want to ask me?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:48.74,0:13:49.26,main,Rishe,0,0,0,,What?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:49.66,0:13:54.11,main,Arnold,0,0,0,,You said that if you won, I'd have \Nto answer one question, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:54.11,0:13:56.27,main,Rishe,0,0,0,,Do you really think I\Ncan ask you like this?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:57.31,0:13:58.27,main,Rishe,0,0,0,,You're laughing?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:58.58,0:14:02.02,main,Rishe,0,0,0,,I knew it! You're having fun \Nwatching my reactions, aren't you?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:02.02,0:14:03.18,main,Arnold,0,0,0,,Am I?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:03.78,0:14:05.91,main,Rishe,0,0,0,,Then, when is your birthday?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:05.91,0:14:08.03,main,Arnold,0,0,0,,The 28th day of the 12th month.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:08.03,0:14:10.97,main,Rishe,0,0,0,,Oh, so you were born in the winter! \NNext, what are your interests?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:10.97,0:14:12.16,main,Arnold,0,0,0,,I don't have any in particular.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:12.16,0:14:14.25,main,Rishe,0,0,0,,What sorts of things do \Nyou like, Your Highness?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:14.25,0:14:16.05,main,Arnold,0,0,0,,I've never really thought about it.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:16.05,0:14:17.84,main,Rishe,0,0,0,,What type of woman do you prefer?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:17.84,0:14:20.27,main,Arnold,0,0,0,,And what are you planning \Nto gain by asking that?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:32.49,0:14:33.85,main,Rishe,0,0,0,,Master Oliver.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:34.33,0:14:36.17,main,Oliver,0,0,0,,Well, well. Lady Rishe.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:36.17,0:14:38.32,main,Rishe,0,0,0,,Are you moving the office now?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:38.32,0:14:42.86,main,Oliver,0,0,0,,Yes. Thank you for preparing such \Na wonderful room for His Highness.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:43.20,0:14:44.18,main,Rishe,0,0,0,,Not at all.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:44.65,0:14:46.48,main,Rishe,0,0,0,,By the way, where is the prince?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:47.03,0:14:50.79,main,Oliver,0,0,0,,Actually, last night he suddenly had \Nto take command of the night watch,
Dialogue: 0,0:14:50.79,0:14:52.12,main,Oliver,0,0,0,,so he hasn't slept yet.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:52.12,0:14:53.17,main,Rishe,0,0,0,,What?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:53.17,0:14:57.20,main,Oliver,0,0,0,,I've implored him to take a nap, but \Nhe has his official duties to perform.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:57.20,0:14:59.52,main,Oliver,0,0,0,,He doesn't show any signs of resting.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:03.91,0:15:06.38,main,Rishe,0,0,0,,Please rest, Your Highness.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:06.38,0:15:09.04,main,Arnold,0,0,0,,Oliver said something unnecessary, didn't he?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:09.04,0:15:11.13,main,Rishe,0,0,0,,Staying up all night \Nwill take its toll on your body.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:11.54,0:15:13.14,main,Arnold,0,0,0,,I won't be able to sleep anyway.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:13.61,0:15:17.95,main,Arnold,0,0,0,,During the day, I can feel all sorts \Nof people's presences in the palace.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:20.35,0:15:21.52,main,Rishe,0,0,0,,All right.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:24.05,0:15:27.84,main,Rishe,0,0,0,,Then I shall lull you \Nto sleep, Prince Arnold.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:28.72,0:15:29.50,main,Arnold,0,0,0,,What?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:36.96,0:15:42.49,main,Rishe,0,0,0,,Now then, I will stay by your side, \Nso please don't worry, just rest.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:44.13,0:15:48.34,main,Arnold,0,0,0,,Sometimes you say things \Nthat make no sense at all.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:48.34,0:15:53.54,main,Rishe,0,0,0,,If I'm here, I don't think you'll \Nbe distracted by far off presences.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:53.54,0:15:55.08,main,Arnold,0,0,0,,You're right about that.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:55.08,0:15:57.89,main,Rishe,0,0,0,,Then please, get some rest.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:23.60,0:16:25.43,main,Rishe,0,0,0,,This doesn't seem to be working.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:29.07,0:16:30.80,main,Rishe,0,0,0,,May I lie by your side?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:38.99,0:16:40.46,main,Rishe,0,0,0,,Pardon the intrusion.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:53.80,0:16:56.44,main,Arnold,0,0,0,,What are you doing?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:56.98,0:17:01.89,main,Rishe,0,0,0,,Imitating a heartbeat like this is a \Ntechnique for calming the heart and mind.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:03.52,0:17:08.14,italics,Rishe; internal,0,0,0,,In my life as a maid, I \Noften used to do this for my lady.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:08.84,0:17:12.96,main,Rishe,0,0,0,,If you do this for a young child, \Nthey'll quickly fall asleep.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:13.45,0:17:14.97,main,Arnold,0,0,0,,A young child?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:18.03,0:17:21.81,main,Arnold,0,0,0,,You're probably the only person \Nwho would treat me like that.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:44.41,0:17:46.27,main,Arnold,0,0,0,,If you're curious about \Nit, do whatever you like.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:02.39,0:18:03.52,main,Arnold,0,0,0,,Stop that.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:04.37,0:18:05.68,main,Arnold,0,0,0,,You really...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:05.68,0:18:09.27,main,Rishe,0,0,0,,I-I'm sorry. That must have tickled.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:11.02,0:18:14.22,main,Arnold,0,0,0,,If we were going to do this, \Nthen I should have worn gloves.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:14.73,0:18:18.56,main,Arnold,0,0,0,,If I had, then I could \Nhave made a counter-stroke.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:18.56,0:18:23.37,main,Rishe,0,0,0,,It isn't as though touching me with gloves \Nor through cloth makes it all right!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:24.31,0:18:25.40,main,Arnold,0,0,0,,It was a joke.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:32.48,0:18:36.40,italics,Rishe; internal,0,0,0,,His Highness is so sincere \Nand oddly conscientious.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:38.68,0:18:41.41,italics,Rishe; internal,0,0,0,,While I, on the other hand...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:46.60,0:18:47.64,main,Rishe,0,0,0,,Please go ahead.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:49.84,0:18:50.86,main,Arnold,0,0,0,,And do what?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:51.71,0:18:53.69,main,Rishe,0,0,0,,I felt I wasn't being fair.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:54.39,0:18:56.86,main,Rishe,0,0,0,,If it would make Your Highness feel better,
Dialogue: 0,0:18:56.86,0:18:59.95,main,Rishe,0,0,0,,then you should touch me \Nand have your reven—
Dialogue: 0,0:18:59.95,0:19:02.54,main,Arnold,0,0,0,,Are you doing this on purpose?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:02.54,0:19:03.87,main,Rishe,0,0,0,,Honestly, Your Highness!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:08.01,0:19:12.30,main,Arnold,0,0,0,,For my revenge... I'll show mercy and \Nsettle for that expression of yours.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:14.80,0:19:16.29,main,Arnold,0,0,0,,You're a strange one.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:16.29,0:19:18.64,main,Arnold,0,0,0,,You think nothing of sleeping beside me,
Dialogue: 0,0:19:18.64,0:19:21.65,main,Arnold,0,0,0,,but meeting my eyes when we're \Nthis close unsettles you.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:23.29,0:19:25.60,main,Rishe,0,0,0,,I wanted to put a charm on you.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:25.60,0:19:26.47,main,Arnold,0,0,0,,A charm?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:26.90,0:19:29.61,main,Rishe,0,0,0,,This palace isn't a battlefield.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:29.61,0:19:31.48,main,Rishe,0,0,0,,It's Your Highness' home, isn't it?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:31.48,0:19:36.86,main,Rishe,0,0,0,,That's why I hoped you would feel even a \Nlittle more at ease so that you could sleep.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:37.45,0:19:40.78,main,Arnold,0,0,0,,Then stay here until I fall asleep.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:42.11,0:19:45.61,main,Arnold,0,0,0,,It's far more pleasant than an empty room.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:48.08,0:19:49.42,main,Rishe,0,0,0,,All right.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:04.68,0:20:05.98,main,Arnold,0,0,0,,You're awake?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:11.56,0:20:13.90,main,Rishe,0,0,0,,Your Highness...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:16.96,0:20:19.15,main,Rishe,0,0,0,,Prince Arnold, why are you here?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:19.15,0:20:22.53,main,Arnold,0,0,0,,Don't you remember climbing \Ninto this bed yourself?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:24.10,0:20:26.55,main,Rishe,0,0,0,,W-Were you able to sleep?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:26.55,0:20:29.18,main,Arnold,0,0,0,,That's the first thing you want to know?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:30.53,0:20:32.40,main,Rishe,0,0,0,,In any case, I do beg your pardon.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:32.40,0:20:34.79,main,Rishe,0,0,0,,I'll leave your room right \Naway. Please don't worry.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:34.21,0:20:34.79,top,Arnold,0,0,0,,Wait.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:35.02,0:20:35.63,main,Rishe,0,0,0,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:36.03,0:20:36.74,main,Rishe,0,0,0,,Wha—
Dialogue: 0,0:20:39.04,0:20:40.30,main,Oliver,0,0,0,,Excuse me, Your Highness!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:40.79,0:20:43.40,main,Arnold,0,0,0,,Stay quiet for just a little while.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:47.05,0:20:47.82,main,Arnold,0,0,0,,Come in.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:50.66,0:20:51.68,main,Arnold,0,0,0,,What's wrong?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:52.10,0:20:56.19,main,Oliver,0,0,0,,We've received reports. Were you sleeping?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:56.19,0:20:59.43,main,Oliver,0,0,0,,Lady Rishe spoke to you, then.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:59.43,0:21:03.20,main,Oliver,0,0,0,,If you're able to spend time \Ncomfortably in your new chambers,
Dialogue: 0,0:21:03.20,0:21:04.45,main,Oliver,0,0,0,,then that's wonderful.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:04.45,0:21:07.32,main,Arnold,0,0,0,,Keep it brief. I'll listen to it here.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:07.87,0:21:09.50,main,Oliver,0,0,0,,As you command.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:12.83,0:21:15.12,main,Oliver,0,0,0,,Then, I'll go back to work.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:15.12,0:21:17.11,main,Oliver,0,0,0,,Please be sure to rest thoroughly.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:17.11,0:21:18.58,main,Arnold,0,0,0,,Stop nagging.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:18.58,0:21:20.35,main,Arnold,0,0,0,,I understand, so hurry up and go away.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:20.35,0:21:21.34,main,Oliver,0,0,0,,Yes, of course.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:21.84,0:21:23.59,main,Oliver,0,0,0,,Well then, good night.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:29.82,0:21:30.84,main,Arnold,0,0,0,,It's all right now.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:31.27,0:21:33.35,main,Rishe,0,0,0,,I-I know.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:33.80,0:21:35.82,main,Rishe,0,0,0,,I know, but...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:44.98,0:21:47.29,main,Elsie,0,0,0,,Welcome back, Lady Rishe.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:47.29,0:21:49.12,main,Rishe,0,0,0,,Thank you, Elsie.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:49.38,0:21:52.09,main,Elsie,0,0,0,,A package has arrived from \Nthe Aria Trading Company.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:52.92,0:21:54.06,main,Rishe,0,0,0,,Thank you.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:01.92,0:22:04.66,italics,Rishe; internal,0,0,0,,Starting tomorrow, I'm going to be very busy.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:07.60,0:22:12.39,main,knight captain,0,0,0,,That will be the ten day training schedule \Nfor all of you knight candidates.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:13.04,0:22:15.14,main,knight captain,0,0,0,,I have high hopes for your progress.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:15.39,0:22:16.52,main,Lucius; knight candidates,0,0,0,,Yes, sir!
